{"tid":351271,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（接受現實）一人一個醜女同靚女既分別","createTime":"2017-08-08T01:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T09:55:49.000Z","uid":45173,"like":40,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aebce73664623a379b78afe3131a912d987ff794","tid":351271,"uid":45173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T01:18:04.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醜女朋友：155cm，做美容中心cold call狗，月入9300，做到隻狗。<br />\n人緣好差，上司日日鬧鳩佢，針對佢既相貌，做左4,5年都無加人工。<br />\n感情方面，A0從來無人追。<br />\n完全活係自己世界裡面，放棄左戀愛。<br />\n<br />\n靚女朋友：165cm，做文員仔，月入15k，準時收工hea到仆街，同事都唔忍心麻煩佢做嘢。<br />\n有4-5個追求者，餐餐有人請。<br />\n上司好鍾意佢，成日話升佢職。<br />\n感情方面，已婚，感情美滿，但都好多人追。<br />\n好多節目，老公成日買一套套護膚品比佢，放工準時報到，唔偷食。<br />\n<br />\n其實兩個工作性質都差不多，甚至係文員更輕鬆。<br />\n但兩位朋友一齊去見工果陣，公司剩係請左靚女朋友。<br />\n果陣醜女朋友就嬲鳩左佢一排，所以話d醜人特別多麻煩事，唔撚識做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f96991cfce61a50967f6fc1f9a005f59499117","tid":351271,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":23,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T01:19:37.000Z","msg":"你咪撚幻想自己有女朋友啦"},{"pid":"bed46fe0d9ec39db6caa90c9946b3131d7203e9f","tid":351271,"uid":45173,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T01:22:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咪撚幻想自己有女朋友啦</blockquote><br />\n訓醒未"},{"pid":"a4f41ffb193937cb8cb6f1adab83fe286a350b21","tid":351271,"uid":82917,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T01:23:15.000Z","msg":"靚女=一句唔該乜撚都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12a54edbc87433da519fe1ae1d409f4dab8affc","tid":351271,"uid":28831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T01:23:24.000Z","msg":"正常"},{"pid":"b59a200460fddacc6c5f688223cbdeb0226b4644","tid":351271,"uid":45173,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T01:25:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靚女=一句唔該乜撚都有<img s